    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Educational toys produced and used in a series for teaching Friedrich Froebel's system of kindergarten education. There are 10 gifts, each comprising one or more geometric shapes and colors.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
